title: Number of people freelancing in U.S. 2014 to 2019
yAxis: Number of people doing freelance work in million
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of people doing freelance work in million. In total the number of data points it has is 6.
Overall Number of people doing freelance work in million has increased over the Year.
Number of people doing freelance work in million is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2017, and lastly roughly constant from 2017 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest Number of people doing freelance work in million, of value 57.3 was reached at Year 2017
The lowest Number of people doing freelance work in million, of value 53.0 was reported at Year 2014
